%N A395892 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {8,6} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395892 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395892 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Index entries for sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395892 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo} = A389936.
%t A395892 (* Cf. A394862 with p=8 and q=6. *)
%Y A395892 Cf. A389936, A393742, A394862.
